<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="keywords" content="12月活动，砸金蛋，积粒,积粒网,91积粒网,返利网,返利,返现,超级返,购物返利,商城返利,淘宝,淘宝返利,京东返利,积分,积分商城,网购返利,91jili.com">
    <meta name="description" content="12月活动，砸金蛋，积粒网，轻松积米粒，快乐换奖励！拥有游戏体验，体验广告，购物返利，商家活动几大板块，网站的货币为米粒，在享受众多商城最优惠价格同时还可从积粒网获得不同比率的现金奖励！积粒网让你省得多，赚得也更多！">
    <title>积粒网-12月活动</title>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css1408/jl.ui.reset.css')}}"/>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css1408/jquery.datetimepicker.css')}}"/>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/jl.ui.Dec.css')}}"/>
    <script src="{{ asset('js/jquery-1.10.2.js')}}" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script src="{{ asset('bundles/fosjsrouting/js/router.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ path('fos_js_routing_js', {"callback": "fos.Router.setData"}) }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js1408/jquery.datetimepicker.js')}}" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js1408/jl.ui.dec.js')}}" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="decTop">
    <div class="decTopCon">
        <div class="logo"><a href="{{ path('_homepage') }}"><img src="{{ asset('images/december/logo.png')}}" width="154" height="42" alt="logo"/></a></div>
        {% if app.session.has('uid') %}
        	<div class="login">{{ app.session.get('nick') }}，[<a href="{{ path('_user_logout') }}" class="logout">退出</a>]</div>
        {% else %}
            <div class="login">您好，请<a href="{{ path('_user_login')}}">登录</a></div>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="timestamp"><img src="{{ asset('images/december/banner.jpg')}}" width="619" height="135"/></span>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="decMain">
    <div class="decMainCon">
        <div class="luckyDraw luckyDrawActive clearfix">
            {% if app.session.has('uid') %}
            <div class="luckyDrawL">
                <div class="noStart"><img src="{{ asset('images/december/noegg.gif')}}" width="466" height="158" alt="您还没有金蛋哦"></div>
                <div class="mask">
                	<div class="hammer"></div>
                    <ul class="goldenEggs clearfix">
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div> 
            {% else %}
            <div class="luckyDrawL">
                <div class="noLogin"><img src="{{ asset('images/december/noegg.gif')}}" width="466" height="158" alt="您还没有金蛋哦"></div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="luckyDrawR">
            	{% if app.session.has('uid') %}
            	<p>您的金蛋：<strong class="eggNum"></strong>个，抢下一个金蛋还差：<strong class="eggMoney"></strong>元</p>
                {% else %}
                <p>您的金蛋：<strong class="eggNum">0</strong>个，抢下一个金蛋还差：<strong class="eggMoney">10</strong>元</p>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="winnerList">
                    <div class="mask">
						{% render(controller("JiliFrontendBundle:DecemberActivity:brokerList") ) %}
                    </div>
                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="decList">
            {% set index_product = 0 %}
            {% for i, row in categorys %}
            <div class="decListMain">
                <h2 class="sort{{ "%02d"|format(i+1) }}">{{ row.categoryName }}<a href="{{ path('jili_frontend_taobao_index') }}">更多>></a></h2>
                <ul class="clearfix">
                    {% for j,product in products[index_product:] if product.taobaoCategory.id  == row.id %}
                    <li><a href="{{ product.clickUrl }}"  target="_blank"><img src="{{ asset(tb_self_promot_pic_path ~ product.pictureName )  }}" alt="产品图片" width="230" height="182" /></a><div class="proIntro"><span class="proDetail"><p><a href="{{ product.clickUrl }}" class="txtLink" target="_blank">{{ product.title }} </a></p><b>￥</b><strong>{{ "%.02f"|format(product.pricePromotion) }}</strong><span>原价：￥{{"%.02f"|format(product.price) }}</span></span><a href="{{ product.clickUrl }}" target="_blank"><span class="bugBtn">点击购买</span></a></span></div></li>
                    {% set index_product = index_product + 1 %}
                    {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="decSort">
            <ul>
                <li class="active">{{ categorys[0].categoryName }}</li>
                {% for i, row in categorys[1:] %}
                <li>{{ row.categoryName }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
                <li><a href="{{ path('jili_frontend_taobao_index') }}">更多商品</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="backTop">回顶部</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="decRule">
	<div class="decRuleBtn">如何抢到金蛋<br/>>></div>
	<div class="decRuleFlow">
        <h2><em>●</em>活动流程</h2>
        <ul class="decRuleCon">
            <li>
            	<p>第<span>1</span>步，抢金蛋</p>
                <div>
                	<p>在<a href="javascript: void(0)" target="_blank">当前页面</a>购物或者到<a href="{{ path('jili_frontend_taobao_index') }}">淘宝专页</a>购物</p>
					<p>购物满10元可得1个金蛋，满50元可得3个金蛋，满150元可得5个金蛋。之后每增加50元就可多得1个金蛋。</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
            	<p>第<span>2</span>步，填写如下表单</p>
                <div class="formWrapper">{% render(controller("JiliFrontendBundle:DecemberActivity:addTaobaoOrder") ) %}</div>
            </li>
            <li>
            	<p>第<span>3</span>步，砸金蛋</p>
               	<div>一等奖<strong>8888</strong>米粒，二等奖<strong>888</strong>米粒，三等奖<strong>88</strong>米粒，还有更多奖励名额等你拿！</div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
{% if  date() > date("2016-1-22 00:00:00")  %}
    <div class="fixMask"></div>
    <div class="endBreak"><div><span class="close"></span><div class="conclusion">来晚一步，砸金蛋活动已经结束了。</div></div></div>
{% else %}
{% endif %}
{% include '::analytics_js.html.twig' %} 
</body>
</html>
